  <title>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">To save and protect lives and maintain the dignity of people living in conflict-affected areas-RCRSS</narrative>
  </title>
  <description type="1">
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">The HPP project will continue to address acute humanitarian needs using cash transfer, distribution of nutritional kits/ NFIs based on assessments, including food security, and strengthening community capacity to support peace at the local level and to prevent and respond to GBV with a focus on building community resilience and conflict transformation capacity, building on experience from the 2016 project as well as the increased focus on Tackling Violence, Building Peace</narrative>
  </description>
